    <section class="section timeline-section">
      <div class="section-label reveal"><span>04</span><p>PROJECT TIMELINE</p></div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <time>2022</time>
          <div>
            <h3>Sign Language Translator and robotics awards</h3>
            <p>I researched communication barriers, completed five interviews, built a Raspberry Pi sign-language translator, received regional and national robotics awards, and completed IBM computer vision coursework.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <time>2023</time>
          <div>
            <h3>Started the Artificial Intelligence degree at PNU</h3>
            <p>I moved to Busan and began my BSc in Artificial Intelligence at Pusan National University.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <time>2024</time>
          <div>
            <h3>DOIT productivity web app</h3>
            <p>I built DOIT, an AI productivity web app using the Claude API and Firebase.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <time>2025</time>
          <div>
            <h3>Gesture-Controlled Smart Glove</h3>
            <p>I built a low-cost wearable prototype using finger bending and hand orientation for cursor control and air-drawing experiments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <time>2026</time>
          <div>
            <h3>NLP, external memory, and embedded systems</h3>
            <p>I worked on NLP, local language-model behavior, external-memory evaluation, and the research architecture for Project RAY.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <time>NEXT</time>
          <div>
            <h3>Next steps for Project RAY</h3>
            <p>I plan to develop short-term and long-term memory, multimodal input, simulation, and the physical humanoid platform. The hardware is still in development.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

